✏️ BACK TO SCHOOL GIVEAWAY ✏️
 
The first day of school is around the corner, and @lunchbots @marleylillykids and @the_happy_planner have teamed up to help one lucky family kick off the year in style, with everything you need to stay organized, prepped, and feeling good from morning drop-off to bedtime routines. 📚🚌💖
 
From personalized gear to lunch-packing essentials and a planner that keeps you one step ahead, this bundle is packed with everything you need to kick off the school year with confidence.
 
🌟 A Large Cinco, Medium Duo, and Small Protein Packer from @lunchbots 
🌟 A personalized backpack and lunch bag from @marleylillykids 
🌟 A planner + sticker set from @the_happy_planner 
 
To enter:
1️⃣ Follow @lunchbots @marleylillykids and @the_happy_planner 
2️⃣ Like this post to show some love
3️⃣ Tag another parent gearing up for back-to-school season in the comments. More comments = more entries!
 
🏆 Bonus Entry: Share to your story and tag us!
 
📆 Giveaway ends at 11:59 pm CT on 7/14/25. Open to continental U.S. residents 18+ only. No purchase is necessary. One winner will be randomly selected and contacted via DM on 7/15/25. This promotion is in no way sponsored, administered by, or associated with Instagram.
